No. 89,

Orig.

California ex rel. State Lands Commission v. United States.

Motion of the United States for judgment on the pleadings is set for oral argument in due course. The defendant shall have 45 days within which to file the opening brief. The brief of the plaintiff shall be filed 30 days after receipt of the opening brief. [For earlier order herein, see ante, p. 809.]
